title: Tomb of the Red Magus
story: The tomb of the Red Magus is situated deep in the dark forest, far from civilization. Currently it is badly infested by beasts.

notes.text: A massive double door with a keyhole on the northern wall.
An eldritch tarot deck hovering in the middle of the large room.
A battered crate with a fish-shaped key in it.
A pile of rubble hides an ancient staff, a mantle and some gold.
Remains of a hobgoblin, a potion of fire breath in his hands.
A trunk holds a wand of force.
